{"approval_requested":0,"approved":1,"beaming":"1","database_id":1343,"db_version":5,"deleted":0,"description":"Smoke detector and motion sensor","device_ref":"0003:000D","exclusion":"<p>Put controller into exclusion mode and access the add\/remove mode by pressing the function button three times within 1.5 seconds. Removing the device will reset it to factory settings.<br><\/p>","first_approval_time":"2021-01-31 17:40:56","frequently_listening":"0","inclusion":"<p>After power is applied, the smoke detector initiates a 1-minute warm-up period.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">During this minute, the device will automatically enter add\/remove mode, and&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">may now be added to the system via the primary controller.<\/span><\/p><p>After the calibration process is finished, you may access the add\/remove mode by pressing the function button three times within 1.5 seconds. Removing the device&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">will reset it to factory settings.<\/span><\/p>","label":"Z-Smoke","last_approval_time":"2021-07-26 19:10:28","listening":"1","overview":"<p>Heatit Z-Smoke Detector is a wireless smoke sensor with built-in PIR motion sensor,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">temperature sensor and emergency light. Heatit Z-Smoke Detector is a wireless&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">operated photo-electronic smoke detector designed to interact with most Z-Wave&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">enabled controllers. The detector features smoke-, temperature-, and IR-detection.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">When other sensors in the Z-Wave network are activated and send an alarm signal,&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">the smoke detector will also sound an alarm with its built-in siren to help give&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">warning.<\/span><\/p>","protocol_version":"6.004","routing":"1","usage":"<p>Function button:<\/p><p>\u2022&nbsp;<spa